能直连 Google？太爽了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/978464", "created": 1696149875, "deleted": 0, "content": "刚到香港两天，买了个 mysim 的移动卡，50G 流量一个月，可以直接 Google ，太爽了！\n\n但是貌似这个卡，回到内地，漫游流量特别贵！\n\n有没有人知道，应该买什么卡，回来之后还梦用，并且流量便宜点，比如 100 一个月 30G 都能接受。\n\n自己也有机场，速度很快，但是就想要这种系统级的出墙！", "content_rendered": "刚到香港两天，买了个 mysim 的移动卡，50G 流量一个月，可以直接 Google ，太爽了！<br /><br />但是貌似这个卡，回到内地，漫游流量特别贵！<br /><br />有没有人知道，应该买什么卡，回来之后还梦用，并且流量便宜点，比如 100 一个月 30G 都能接受。<br /><br />自己也有机场，速度很快，但是就想要这种系统级的出墙！", "last_modified": 1696176367, "replies": 24, "id": 978464}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 39647, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281", "stars": 5538, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 89233, "username": "yxc", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yxc", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d788/aa5c/89233_mini.png?m=1422705024", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d788/aa5c/89233_normal.png?m=1422705024", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d788/aa5c/89233_large.png?m=1422705024", "created": 1419954667, "last_modified": 1422705024}, "last_reply_by": "WhatTheBridgeSay", "last_touched": 1696186569, "title": "运营商级 骚扰短信 拦截关键词分享。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/978414", "created": 1696130061, "deleted": 0, "content": "各种广告短信现在已经被运营商和各类拦截 app 清理的差不多了。\r\n\r\n但是各种破单位的公益短信借着运营商的号码开始狂轰滥炸，天天发天天发。\r\n\r\n整理了一下半年以来收到的拦截关键词\r\n1.iPhone 推荐使用熊猫吃短信，把不过滤 5 位数号码的勾去掉，然后输入以下关键词\r\n2.安卓的默认应该有短信禁止关键词功能，MIUI 路径如下：短信-右上角齿轮-骚扰拦截-短信拦截-关键词黑名单\r\n\r\n![IMG_6890.png]( https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/e7XKCMaYycJG9vN.png)\r\n![IMG_6889.png]( https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/yZ1XdF4rCTveBNo.png)\r\n![IMG_6891.png]( https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/AvYaQcikPTGbxBp.png)", "content_rendered": "<p>各种广告短信现在已经被运营商和各类拦截 app 清理的差不多了。</p>\n<p>但是各种破单位的公益短信借着运营商的号码开始狂轰滥炸，天天发天天发。</p>\n<p>整理了一下半年以来收到的拦截关键词\n1.iPhone 推荐使用熊猫吃短信，把不过滤 5 位数号码的勾去掉，然后输入以下关键词\n2.安卓的默认应该有短信禁止关键词功能，MIUI 路径如下：短信-右上角齿轮-骚扰拦截-短信拦截-关键词黑名单</p>\n<p><img alt=\"IMG_6890.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/e7XKCMaYycJG9vN.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"IMG_6889.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/yZ1XdF4rCTveBNo.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"IMG_6891.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/01/AvYaQcikPTGbxBp.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1696131465, "replies": 24, "id": 978414}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 211491, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3972, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 465902, "username": "allAboutDbmss", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/allAboutDbmss", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/768eb37d1b27ae383484fb24b43bd5e0?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/768eb37d1b27ae383484fb24b43bd5e0?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/768eb37d1b2